### Crear usuario (pre-requisito)
# @name createUser
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Juan Perez - Piloto",
  "type": "premium"
}

### Crear carrera (pre-requisito)
# @name createRace
POST http://localhost:3000/api/races
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "raceDateTime": "2025-09-15T14:00:00",
  "result": "pending",
  "description": "Gran Premio de Argentina",
  "registrationDeadline": "2025-09-10T23:59:59",
  "combinationId": 1
}

### IDs para las pruebas
@userId = {{createUser.response.body.data.id}}
@raceId = {{createRace.response.body.data.id}}

### Obtener todas las inscripciones a carreras
GET http://localhost:3000/api/race-users

### Crear inscripción a carrera
# @name createRaceUser
POST http://localhost:3000/api/race-users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "registrationDateTime": "2025-09-01T10:30:00",
  "startPosition": 5,
  "finishPosition": 3,
  "raceId": {{raceId}},
  "userId": {{userId}}
}

### ID de la inscripción
@raceUserId = {{createRaceUser.response.body.data.id}}

### Obtener una inscripción por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/race-users/{{raceUserId}}

### Actualizar una inscripción
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/race-users/{{raceUserId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "registrationDateTime": "2025-09-01T10:30:00",
  "startPosition": 5,
  "finishPosition": 1,
  "raceId": {{raceId}},
  "userId": {{userId}}
}

### Actualizar solo la posición final
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/race-users/{{raceUserId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "finishPosition": 2
}

### Eliminar una inscripción
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/race-users/{{raceUserId}}